  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1001760/extras/8f961cb4d065c195e73b76e304790663.avif?t=1647113501\" width=600 height=340 /></span><br><br>Dreaming of snow slopes? Then this game is for you! Snowboard and try various tracks! You will like race against the clock mode. It will give you a chance to prove that you are faster than the wind, that no obstacle will stop you.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features:</h2><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Race against the clock mode;<br></li><li>Great atmosphere due to the first-person mode;<br></li><li>A variety of skins for your board.</li></ul><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1001760/extras/c1daa4f0fa216f28f380ef4fdee92602.avif?t=1647113501\" width=600 height=340 /></span>",
